{
  "title": "Condition → condition_occurrence / domain routing",
  "notes": "Branch: the Condition stage-1 view (mapspec/views/Condition__condition_occurrence.view.json) fans out one staging row per `code.coding[] | evidence.concept.coding[]`. The shared resolve pass (mapspec/etl/_resolve_condition.sql) walks each coding's system through cm.fhir_system_to_omop_vocab → vocab.concept (source) → 'Maps to' → vocab.concept (standard, standard_concept='S'), then DISTINCT ON (id, std.concept_id) collapses multiple codings of the same Condition that resolve to the same standard concept (ORDER BY prefers SNOMED so the surviving src_* columns come from the already-standard vocab). Each surviving row carries std_domain. The four per-domain stage-2 ETLs then filter by std_domain: 'Condition'→condition_occurrence, 'Observation'→observation, 'Procedure'→procedure_occurrence, 'Measurement'→measurement. Surrogate PK = stringToId(Condition.id || '|' || std_concept_id) (omitted from expected rows — derived). person_id / visit_occurrence_id / provider_id are referenceToId() FK hashes asserted symbolically as ref:.\n\nKEY MAPPING RULES (from Condition__condition_occurrence.sql):\n- condition_concept_id = std_concept_id; condition_source_concept_id = src_concept_id; condition_source_value = left(COALESCE(code_display, src_code, code_text),50).\n- dates: start = COALESCE(onset.ofType(dateTime), onset.ofType(Period).start, recordedDate); end = COALESCE(abatement.ofType(dateTime), abatement.ofType(Period).end). Cast ::date and ::timestamp (wall-clock, NOT UTC-converted — the offset is dropped, not applied).\n- condition_type_concept_id = COALESCE(cm.fhir_condition_category_to_omop[category.first().coding.first().code], 32817). encounter-diagnosis→32827, problem-list-item→32840, health-concern→32817.\n- condition_status_concept_id = COALESCE(NULLIF(verificationStatus_target,0), NULLIF(clinicalStatus_target,0), 0): verificationStatus PREFERRED over clinicalStatus. confirmed→32893, provisional→32899 (else 0); clinicalStatus only 'resolved'→32906 (everything else→0).\n- EXCLUSION: WHERE COALESCE(verificationStatus,'confirmed') NOT IN ('refuted','entered-in-error') — applies to ALL four domain ETLs.\n- stop_reason = left(abatement.ofType(string),20); condition_status_source_value = left(clinicalStatus.coding.first().code,50).\n- provider_id = COALESCE(referenceToId(asserter), referenceToId(recorder)).\n\nAll concept_ids verified live in vocab.concept (v20260227 bundle): 320128 Essential hypertension (SNOMED 59621000, Condition, S), 35207668 Essential (primary) hypertension (ICD10CM I10, Condition, non-standard, Maps-to 320128), 4199788 Medication review due (SNOMED 314529007, Observation, S), 32827 EHR encounter record (Type Concept), 32840 EHR problem list (Type Concept), 32893 Confirmed diagnosis (Condition Status), 32906 Resolved condition (Condition Status). Constant gender/birthDate held fixed across variants so the verificationStatus / domain / coding dimensions are the only diffs.",
